msgctxt "talk00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Since you're a traveler, you should\n"
"probably know this:\n"
"\n"
"On the other side of <2.se_co>Mount Drena<3.re_co>,\n"
"northeast of this stable, there are\n"
"<4.se_co>ruins that are dark even during the day<5.re_co>!\n"
"I've never met anyone who's been in\n"
"there, so either no one has ever gone\n"
"in...or no one has ever come out!\n"
"Or maybe I just haven't met everyone\n"
"yet...<6.pa> But in any case, you'd best forget\n"
"about going in there!\n"
"<7.so><8.te_si><9.se_co>You should probably stay here forever just to be\n"
"safe.<10.pa> Teehee!<11.re_co><12.te_si><13.se_co><14.pa><15.re_co>"
msgstr ""

