msgctxt "talk01"
msgid ""
"It's just common sense that traveling\n"
"dark roads at night is dangerous!<1.pa>\n"
"\n"
"But on the other side of <2.se_co>Mount Drena<3.re_co>,\n"
"northeast of this stable, there are\n"
"<4.se_co>ruins that are dark even during the day<5.re_co>!\n"
"<6.so>But no one who has gone there has\n"
"ever come back!<7.pa> So you'd best forget\n"
"about going there!\n"
"<8.so><9.se_co><10.te_si>You could always...stay here with me "
"forever.<11.pa>\n"
"Teehee...<12.pa><13.te_si><14.re_co>"
msgstr ""

