msgctxt "talk02"
msgid ""
"Nothing to do in this weather but stay\n"
"here at <1.se_co>Serenne Stable <2.re_co>and relax.\n"
"\n"
"That's probably why these <3.se_co>leviathan<4.re_co>\n"
"researchers are here at the stable.\n"
"\n"
"<5.so><6.se_co><7.te_si>And because they TOTALLY have a thing for me...\n"
"Teehee!<8.te_si><9.re_co>"
msgstr ""

